But here.

19:06.989 --> 19:08.626
Maybe you can hug this...

19:08.627 --> 19:10.373
- Ohh!
- ...Until you get home to him.

19:11.230 --> 19:13.093
- Thank you!
- (Chuckling)

19:17.135 --> 19:18.869
You could do this for a living.

19:18.870 --> 19:20.428
(Chuckles)

19:22.559 --> 19:24.337
Merry Christmas, Ben.

19:25.423 --> 19:27.244
Merry Christmas to you too.

19:28.151 --> 19:30.680
Special delivery for the wheelers!

19:31.461 --> 19:33.165
- Emma!
- Ho ho ho, everyone!

19:33.805 --> 19:35.000
Here's your daddy.

19:35.001 --> 19:36.171
Hi!

19:36.713 --> 19:38.902
Mom, I'm so happy you're here. I'm sorry...

19:39.203 --> 19:40.641
I screwed everything up.

19:41.126 --> 19:42.622
(Sighs) I can't believe I thought a toy

19:42.623 --> 19:44.198
would make Christmas perfect.

19:44.540 --> 19:46.166
It's okay, Benji.

19:46.167 --> 19:50.026
You're not the only one who went
a little nuts this holiday season.

19:50.027 --> 19:52.220
It took seeing a cup
full of Christmas crazy

19:52.221 --> 19:54.050
for me to realize what's
really important...

19:54.733 --> 19:56.324
just being with my family.

19:57.286 --> 20:00.464
Yeah, you were a
little fa-LA-LA-looney.

20:00.465 --> 20:01.476
(Laughing)

20:01.477 --> 20:03.451
I was talking about Riley.

20:04.440 --> 20:06.904
But I don't understand
how you guys got here.

20:07.270 --> 20:09.180
The roads were all closed
because of the storm.

20:09.181 --> 20:11.058
What are you talking about?
They were totally clear.

20:11.059 --> 20:13.778
- I was going like 90. (Laughs)
- It was awesome.

20:14.369 --> 20:16.200
Wait, there aren't any
cops in here, are there?

20:17.369 --> 20:18.897
Hey, where's Santa?

20:18.898 --> 20:20.239
He's right over...

20:21.394 --> 20:23.012
huh, that's weird.

20:23.671 --> 20:25.119
He didn't even say goodbye.

20:28.231 --> 20:29.524
Don't worry.

20:29.958 --> 20:31.348
If we need him...

20:31.837 --> 20:33.934
I have a feeling he'll find us.

20:33.935 --> 20:36.288
(Chuckles) Merry Christmas, Emma.

