20:46.785 --> 20:48.785
♪ Make it full of cheer

20:48.786 --> 20:49.874
Big finish!

20:49.875 --> 20:53.216
♪ Make it full of cheer!

20:53.631 --> 20:54.787
- (Cheers and applause)
- Yah!

20:59.294 --> 21:00.849
I'm sorry!

21:02.642 --> 21:05.822
Well, boss, those
Wheelers were a tough one,

21:05.823 --> 21:08.578
but I think we pulled it off.

21:08.579 --> 21:10.360
So, should we go get some dinner?

21:10.361 --> 21:11.583
Oh, no need.

21:11.584 --> 21:13.496
I got us a ham.

21:13.965 --> 21:15.563
(Laughing) Ho ho ho ho!

